<http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.rbe.2017.03.002>
    dc:creator "Castillo, Stephanie", "Dikow, Torsten" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic revision of Plyomydas Wilcox & Papavero, 1971 with the description of two new species and its transfer to Mydinae (Insecta: Diptera: Mydidae)" ;
    bibo:endPage "202" ;
    bibo:issue "2" ;
    bibo:journal "Revista Brasileira de Entomologia" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2017-03-24" ;
    bibo:startPage "192" ;
    bibo:volume "61" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10112825>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10112829>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10112831> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10112825>
    dc:description "Figs.12–14. Photographsof male Plyomydas peruviensis (AAM-003731):(12) dorsal (Morphbank #860772); (13) same,lateral (#860774); (14) same,headanterior (#860776). Scale line= 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10112825/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10112829>
    dc:description "Figs. 21–26. Male terminalia of Plyomydas species: (21) Plyomydas peruviensis (AAM-003729), lateral; (22) same, dorsal; (23) same, ventral; (24) Plyomydas phalaros sp. nov. paratype (CASENT8380022), lateral; (25) same, dorsal; (26) same, ventral. Scale line =1 mm, setation omitted. Figshare DOI 10.6084/m9.figshare.4490474." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10112829/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10112831>
    dc:description "Fig. 27. Map of South America with elevational relief and biodiversity hotspots (in grey) showing distribution of Plyomydas adelphe sp. nov. (orange), P. peruviensis (yellow), and P. phalaros sp. nov. (blue). Type localities plotted with square symbols. Map data available in Google Earth KML file 6102and also through GBIF (data-set 7f2de377-9f9f-4276-b0b8-5c792b499223, DOI 10.15468/tiymja)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10112831/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

